data.meta_description: The official University of Michigan Hall of Honor for the Michigan Wolverines
data.text:
2023 Hall of Honor Class

• 2023 HOH Central | Announcement

2023 Induction Class (from left): April Fronzoni Bertin, Ryan Bertin, Justin Toman, Tiffany Ofili Porter, Ron Warhurst and Peter Vanderkaay

2022 Hall of Honor Class

• 2022 HOH Central | Announcement

2022 Induction Class (from left): Abby Crumpton Minihan, Debbie Williams-Hoak, Jim Richardson, Larry Simmons (son of Red Simmons), Ellen Tomek, Samantha Findlay and Sam Williams (grandson of Joan Spillane-Postma)

2020 Hall of Honor Class

• 2020 HOH Central | Announcement

2020 Induction Class (from left): Sarah Cain (gymnastics), Jim Paciorek (baseball), S.A. Tripp Welborne III (football), Lexi Zimmerman (volleyball), Kelli Gannon (field hockey) with Athletic Director Warde Manuel. Not pictured: Ty Law (football)

2019 Hall of Honor Class

• 2019 HOH Central | Announcement

2019 Induction Class (from left): Rick Downes and Donna Knox (children of Hal Downes), John Fisher, Lara Hooiveld, Ron Simpkins, Erick Anderson, Nick Willis and Stacey Thomas.
